Name: City Name
Remarks:
L010203: If MS1-01 is present, then at least one of MS1-02 or MS1-03 is required
E0104: Only one of MS1-01 or MS1-04 may be present

Name: State or Province Code
Notes: Code (Standard State/Province) as defined by appropriate government agency
Remarks: C0201: If MS1-02 is present, then MS1-01 is required

Name: Country Code
Remarks: C0301: If MS1-03 is present, then MS1-01 is required

Name: Longitude Code
Notes: Code indicating the longitude in degrees (3 positions), minutes (2 positions), and seconds (2 positions)
Remarks:
P0405: If either MS1-04 or MS1-05 is present, then the other is required
MS104 is the longitude expressed in Degrees, Minutes, and Seconds.

Name: Latitude Code
Notes: Code indicating the latitude in degrees (3 positions), minutes (2 positions), seconds (2 positions)
Remarks: MS105 is the latitude expressed in Degrees, Minutes, and Seconds.

Name: Direction Identifier Code
Remarks:
C0604: If MS1-06 is present, then MS1-04 is required
MS106 may only be 'E' or 'W'.

Name: Direction Identifier Code
Remarks:
C0705: If MS1-07 is present, then MS1-05 is required
MS107 may only be 'N' or 'S'.
